title: Chicken Sausage & Farro Soup with Herb Butter Toasts
description: Rain or shine, warm or cool, it’s tough not to crave a big bowl of soup (i.e. the culinary equivalent of a bear hug). Tonight’s soup is chock-full of goodness—that is to say spiced chicken sausage, fresh tomato, chewy farro, and a swirl of Parmesan cheese. And because no good brothy bowl is complete without some bread for dunking, we’re also throwing in buttery, herby toast points. Get ready for a meal as satisfying as it is delicious.
